{
  "stem": "13524.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a very meager excuse for us, to get to-- to Majdanek or-- or-- we were very lucky, because in the house where we live, there was somebody who had certain information, or from outside, or knew somebody in Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we knew before-- that I remember clearly at one stage, it was the ghetto to be liquidated-- to made smaller.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said that they're coming in the morning, and they will collect lots of Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was in thousands.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was not just a few hundred or hundred-- a lots of Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my parents decided we're going before, out of the ghetto, and stay overnight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we will see what following day will bring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, surely, following day, I was sent to my mother's friend, out of the ghetto, but in the path of the transport.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at one stage, the lady in whose house I was staying-- she told me, I saw your parents going into the transport.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So you better go and join them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But, of course, I knew better than that, because I knew where my parents were hidden.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They told us, you go to such-and-such a woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We going to this fellow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My sister is going down there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We distributed ourselves.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I knew where they were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They couldn't have been in a transport, because they were out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I didn't tell her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And when she told me, you better go, I felt the situation is dangerous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She's going to tell somebody that I'm hiding here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She had sewing machine and few bits and pieces, and that was important for her, that I should not stay behind.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because, God forbid, mother may ask for the sewing machine or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was the attitude of Poles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes-- and other things.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
